replies.author: 森林蝙蝠
replies.txt_content:
net.minecraftforge.fml.common.LoaderExceptionModCrash: Caught exception from Armory Expansion - Construct's Armory (armoryexpansion-conarm)
Caused by: slimeknights.tconstruct.library.TinkerAPIException: [TCon API] Could not add Trait to "xu_demonic_metal": Trait "xu_whispering" was already registered by Unknown
conarm和armory expansion都注册了exu2的恶魔锭，所以就重复冲突了，解决办法是删除其一，或者查看mod配置文件删除其对恶魔锭的注册（如果有）。
@李j  @ItIsEnderman
